== Demo App for integrating CouchDB and Sunspot

* bundle install
* start your engines aka rake sunspot:solr:run or sunspot:solr:start
* run the server
* add some data
* and search for it

== Known issues

* seems like the reindex task is not working correctly

== References

https://github.com/outoftime/sunspot
